> Include: common.catala_en

```catala
scope S:
  definition z equals [
    Structure { -- i: 3 -- e: Int content x };
    Structure { -- i: 4 -- e: y };
    Structure { -- i: 5 -- e: Dat content |1970-01-01| }
  ]
  definition a equals number of (z ++ 1.1) / 2
```

